        <title>BRAKE PADS</title>
        <para>The brake pads should be replaced whenever they are found to be worn to 3/16 inch (4.76 mm) of brake pad
            material thickness from the brake pad backing plate. Refer to GROUP 04-CALIPER DISC BRAKES and DIAMOND LIFE&#8482;
            (BOSCH PIN SLIDE) DISC BRAKES in the CTS-5000 Master Service Manual.
        </para>
